cscie97.asn4.knowledge.engine

Class KnowledgeGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn4.knowledge.engine.KnowledgeGraph

  • public class KnowledgeGraph
extends java.lang.Object
    The KnowledgeGraph is responsible for managing the set of active triples. The triples are stored in memory and not persisted. The KnowledgeGraph is a singleton.
